→ We have implemented two global campaigns addressing contributing factors of injuries and mental health. We also address psychosocial risks in our EHS Hazards Identi- fication, Risk Assessment, and Risk Control (HIRARC) pro- cess.

→ In addition, Siemens’ regional companies and business units have developed a variety of initiatives, including regular “Health Talks,” learning and action weeks, and “Safety Focus Days.”

